{"tid":263893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[支那狗夢想世界第一]柯潔稱多次夢到自己反勝AlphaGo","createTime":"2017-05-30T11:32:08.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-30T17:23:23.000Z","uid":54373,"like":7,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"17ae92d911747e7bd1196bd38a9019c46758fdf0","tid":263893,"uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:32:08.000Z","msg":"排名世界第一的中國九段棋手柯潔日前以0比3慘敗給人工智能程式AlphaGo後，便飛往南韓參加LG杯世界棋王戰。他今日接受韓媒採訪時透露，在「人機大戰」後他曾連續喝酒9小時，僅僅睡了兩小時，卻多次夢到自己擊敗AlphaGo。<br />\n<br />\n柯潔透露，為了擊敗AlphaGo，他曾仔細研究AlphaGo在網上的60連勝棋譜，惜未見成效。而在上周六最後一局「人機大戰」後，他想到自己沒能發揮得更好，導致了完敗，太難過了所以留淚。 <br />\n<br />\n另外，柯潔又稱，上周六連敗3場後，平時不愛喝酒的他，在古力等前輩棋手陪伴下，從下午6時便開始喝酒，一直喝到翌日凌晨3時。由於他當日凌晨6時便要坐飛機趕往南韓，故他只睡了兩個小時，但他卻夢見自己戰勝AlphaGo，笑稱︰「雖然在夢裏贏過，但現實中是全敗，很傷心。今後估計也會經常夢到。」"},{"pid":"59188287be0f006fb9b999aa526e0a4dbb3696ba","tid":263893,"uid":89931,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:49:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2383ed5fc516e74636819e7a942ae68683aa4987","tid":263893,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:51:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec21b591a887edded0620f16eb29b5543404b7e2","tid":263893,"uid":13592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:54:52.000Z","msg":"取消資格<br />\n<br />\n老友看見我　也會驚訝<br />\n平日杯酒不沾　今晚總喝不厭<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ec593f5e6782df32decf0f0041a187dec226742","tid":263893,"uid":40628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T11:57:17.000Z","msg":"其實一個咁蠢嘅人點解可以成為圍棋高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"026766ed7c3066501947889cae6516b7f8f1b5a9","tid":263893,"uid":55581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:00:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實一個咁蠢嘅人點解可以成為圍棋高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因住又比大中華膠同五毛圍你，話佢咁都係人之常情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39b996790917b29e22813cc197e2af732f1b07e3","tid":263893,"uid":36084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實一個咁蠢嘅人點解可以成為圍棋高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因住又比大中華膠同五毛圍你，話佢咁都係人之常情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人類最後希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a60fe594ded64076a1df76b42b73a0c5ce89a8","tid":263893,"uid":53705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實一個咁蠢嘅人點解可以成為圍棋高手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢只係喜歡亂講野, 但唔係蠢<br />\n<br />\n正如 菲律賓果個總統都成日亂講野, 唔通又代表佢蠢咩"},{"pid":"ab553a70ad68f0ba90f31aafb5b723282c0e8b97","tid":263893,"uid":75533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:05:41.000Z","msg":"睇得出佢真係好灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8c1f73f557de27aaf5aa4aeacf17e00b80bf915","tid":263893,"uid":70629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:11:42.000Z","msg":"悟空~ 發夢無咁早..."},{"pid":"df4e4aa3ee8025f7c9114bb3db701e9f984dad79","tid":263893,"uid":9348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T12:18:31.000Z","msg":"垃鳩圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d182a9769702358b6f8f83d899884a921cacc049","tid":263893,"uid":9348,"like":0,"d